# 2. Heart-Shaped Memory Matching Game

## Purpose

A **heart-shaped memory card matching game** where players flip image cards and match photo pairs.

## Layout Features

* Full-screen dark background
* Centered game board inside a `.game` container
* Custom heart-shaped board layout
* Decorative heading:

  * `Match the photo pairs`
* Footer-style credit text
* Hidden surprise modal shown after game completion
* Restart button in the HUD

## Game Board

* Grid-based layout with **9 columns**
* Empty cells used to form a heart shape
* Card size and spacing controlled with CSS variables
* Responsive layout

## Card Features

* Each card is a button element
* Includes:

  * front face
  * back face with image
* 3D flip animation using `rotateY(180deg)`
* Matched cards remain flipped
* Matched cards get different shadow styling
* Empty spaces are inserted for heart design

## Game Logic

* Images are defined in `pairImages`
* Each image is duplicated to create a pair
* Cards are shuffled before rendering
* Players can flip two cards at a time
* Matching cards:

  * stay flipped
  * increase match count
* Non-matching cards flip back after a delay
* Same card cannot be selected twice
* Matched cards cannot be clicked again
* Board is locked while checking a turn

## HUD / Progress

* Displays **Moves**
* Displays **Matches**
* Updates dynamically
* Restart resets the full game

## Completion Surprise

* A hidden modal appears when all pairs are matched
* Uses fade and visibility transitions
* Includes a close button
* Final heading/message area exists but is currently commented out

## Secret Cheat Code

* Keyboard sequence: `A`, `B`, `C`
* Reveals and auto-matches all remaining pairs
* Runs pair-by-pair with animation
* Does not run if already active or if the game is complete

## Accessibility

* Board has `aria-label="Memory card game board"`
* Cards have `aria-label="Memory card"`
* Uses semantic button elements

## Responsive Features

### Below 900px

* Smaller card size
* Adjusted side text size
* Reduced spacing

### Below 640px

* Vertical scrolling enabled
* Mobile-friendly layout
* Side text becomes centered
* Credit moves into normal document flow

## Technical Notes

* Right-side heading is commented out
* Surprise modal message is commented out
* Only the close button is visible in the modal by default
* Images are expected as local assets such as `a1.jpg`, `a2.jpg`, etc.

---

# 3. Ramadan Mubarak Gallery Page

## Purpose

A **Ramadan Mubarak-themed image gallery page** with a festive loader, lightbox, confetti, emoji click effects, music, and decorative visuals.

## Setup

* **Page title:** `Ramadan Mubarak - Image Gallery`
* **External Libraries:**

  * GSAP
  * canvas-confetti
  * Three.js
* **Google Fonts:**

  * Amiri
  * Poppins
* **External CSS:**

  * `Emoji animation.css`
  * `heart floatUp.css`

## Loader Screen

A full-screen GSAP animated loader includes:

* moon icon
* `Ramadan Mubarak` title
* animated bouncing dots
* progress bar
* rotating loading messages:

  * `Loading blessings...`
  * `Preparing spiritual journey...`
  * `Arranging prayers...`
  * `Almost ready...`

Main content remains hidden until loading completes.

## Hero Header

* Main heading: `Ramadan Mubarak`
* Subtitle: `Blessed Month of Fasting, Prayer, and Reflection`
* Decorative moon via CSS `::before`
* Gradient header on small screens
* `hero.jpg` background on screens wider than 667px
* Entrance animation with `fadeInDown`

## Stars Feature

* `#stars-container` exists in the header
* Stars support:

  * twinkling animation
  * hover scaling
  * pointer interaction
* Star behavior likely handled in external script `star-msg.js`

## Gallery

* Responsive flexbox layout
* Thumbnail size: `200px × 200px`
* Rounded corners and shadows
* Hover scale effect
* Golden glowing hover shadow

## Gallery Content

Includes **30 day-based items**:

* `A1.jpg` to `A30.gif`

### Final Item

* `A30.gif` is wrapped in a link to an external Canva page

## Lightbox

* Fullscreen modal viewer
* Dark patterned background using `ramadan-pattern.png`
* Includes:

  * close button
  * enlarged image
  * caption
* Image effects:

  * zoom-in animation
  * glowing border
  * shimmer effect
  * animated shadow glow

## Music

* Background audio: `Aaa1.mp3`
* Loop enabled
* After loader:

  * volume set to `0.5`
  * autoplay attempted
* If blocked, failure is logged in console

## Click Effects

### Confetti

* Clicking anywhere triggers confetti
* Uses:

  * 100 particles
  * spread of 70

### Floating Emojis

* 3 emojis appear per click
* Randomly selected from:

  * ❤️
  * 💖
  * 💘
  * 😊
  * 😘
  * 💞
  * 🥰
  * 🌸
* Randomized placement and animation duration
* Removed automatically after 2 seconds

## Decorative Dynamic Elements

The page includes placeholders for:

* `#love-message`
* `#stars-container`
* `#hearts`

External scripts suggest support for:

* dynamic background color
* heart generation
* lightbox behavior
* audio handling
* security restrictions
* star messages
* custom messages

## Technical Notes

* Three.js is loaded but not used directly in this file
* Lightbox logic depends on external script `Lightbox functionality.js`
* Several effects are implied through external JavaScript files

