# 5. Eid al-Adha Greeting Page

## Purpose

An **Eid al-Adha greeting message page** with romantic visuals and an interactive animated particle background.

## Setup

* **Page title:** `Eid Mubarak!🌙❤️`
* **Google Fonts:**

  * Dancing Script
  * Poppins

## Design

* Full-screen greeting page
* Dark romantic gradient background
* Centered glassmorphism message card
* Soft red, pink, and white palette

## Greeting Content

* Main heading:

  * `Eid Mubarak, My Love! 🌙`
* Personalized message paragraph
* Extra blessing line
* Signature:

  * `Forever Yours,`
* Additional note in a `<pre>` block:

  * `i even don't know you read ,this message or not .still i writting this`

## Visual Elements

### Message Card

* Semi-transparent dark background
* Blur effect with `backdrop-filter`
* Rounded corners
* Shadow
* Light border tint
* Animated scale + fade entrance

### Moon Decoration

* Radial gradient moon
* Glow effect
* Fade-in animation
* Floating motion

### Particle Canvas Background

* Fullscreen fixed canvas
* Animated hearts and stars
* Randomized:

  * position
  * size
  * speed
  * color
  * rotation

### Particle Colors

* `#ff6b6b`
* `#ffa3a3`
* `#ffd3d3`
* `#f8f9fa`
* `#fff`

## Click Interaction

* Clicking the canvas creates burst particles
* 10 additional particles per click
* Click particles move outward and fade away

## Responsive Features

### On screens 768px and above

* Larger heading
* Larger paragraph text
* Increased card padding
* Larger moon
* Larger signature
* Larger `<pre>` text

## Technical Notes

* Canvas resizes with the window
* Animation runs with `requestAnimationFrame`
* Click particles are effectively updated twice per frame
* CSS exists for `.hidden-message`, `.hearts-btn`, and `.mosque`, but those elements are not present in the HTML

