## 6.4 “The Code of Love” Page

### Purpose

A **romantic love-letter themed page** with typed code-style text, animated heart canvas, audio, and a downloadable image action.

### Setup

* **Page title:** `card`
* Loads:

  * Font Awesome
  * `default.css`
  * `jquery.js`
  * `garden.js`
  * `functions.js`
* Custom font:

  * `digit` from `digital-7_mono.ttf`

### Features

* Autoplay audio:

  * `goodby.mp3`
* Split layout:

  * left code-message area
  * right heart/canvas area
* Typewriter text reveal using:

  * `$("#code").typewriter();`
* Download button triggers:

  * `Screenshot 2025-06-23 9.11.33 PM.png`
* Download filename set to:

  * `filename.jpg`
* Heart canvas animation inside:

  * `#loveHeart`
  * `#garden`
* Personalized text includes:

  * `MISS SAIBA ARSHAD`
  * `I LOVE YOU SO MUCH`
  * `- STUPID`
* Live elapsed-time counter starts from:

  * September 5, 2016 at 16:30:00
* Heart animation starts after 5 seconds
* Includes canvas support fallback logic

